            <title>[LU-8205] Support RHEL 6.8 on b2_5_fe</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8205</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We need support for RHEL 6.8 on b2_5_fe.  This needs to be implemented in a way that cleanly integrates with the RHEL 7 support in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6843&quot; title=&quot;Support RHEL7 on b2_5_fe&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6843&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6843&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

